&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Easyship:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Easyship is one of the world&#39;s leading multi-carrier shipping software, built to make global eCommerce borderless. Since 2014, we&#39;ve been on a mission to democratize logistics by removing the &quot;black box&quot; of international shipping costs and complexities. Trusted by over 100,000 brands, our platform provides a single &quot;mission control&quot; for global trade, offering access to 550+ courier services across 200+ destinations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;We are an award-winning, global team (Forbes 30 Under 30, TechInAsia&#39;s Best Startup) with offices in London, New York, Hong Kong, and beyond. We&#39;re growing fast, we value transparency, and we genuinely enjoy building the infrastructure that powers modern commerce. If you&#39;re ready to solve complex problems at scale, we&#39;d love to have you join us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Account Executive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;: Europe (Remote)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Relationships: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sales Team, Customers, Marketing, Customer Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Easyship is a shipping technology platform that connects sellers and marketplaces to couriers, and we build customized end-to-end logistics solutions for the world&#39;s fastest-growing brands. As our pipeline grows, we need closers who can turn qualified opportunities into happy, scaling customers. We&#39;re looking for an Account Executive who knows eCommerce and shipping, runs a tight sales process, and loves the work of discovery, demo, and close. You&#39;ll own a book of business from first conversation to signed deal, helping merchants solve real logistics problems with Easyship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What would you be responsible for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Owning the full sales cycle for your accounts, from qualification and discovery through demo, negotiation, and close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Building and managing a healthy pipeline through a mix of inbound leads and self-sourced outbound prospecting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Running consultative discovery to understand each merchant&#39;s shipping, warehousing, and fulfillment needs, and mapping Easyship&#39;s solution to them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Delivering compelling product demos and ROI-based business cases that move deals forward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Negotiating commercial terms and closing deals to consistently hit and exceed quota.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Working collaboratively with global teams across sales engineering, onboarding, and customer success to ensure a smooth handoff and strong customer start.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Keeping CRM

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Easyship:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Easyship is a leading global shipping software and API platform&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;trusted by 100,000+ eCommerce merchants to compare couriers, automate fulfilment, and simplify cross-border shipping, taxes and duties. A top-rated Shopify Certified Technology Provider, eBay preferred fulfilment partner, and Amazon preferred multi-channel integrator, Easyship is the G2 category leader (April 2026), offering 550+ courier services worldwide. We believe in accelerating borderless commerce through innovative solutions, and we&#39;re proud that brands of all sizes from small business to enterprise trust Easyship for all their shipping needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Business Development Executive for our Enterprise Outbound Team. Their primary focus will be owning the full sales cycle for warehousing, fulfilment, and shipping software solutions, from initial outreach through to close. They will work closely with outbound leads across e-commerce and marketplace businesses, particularly those operating in or shipping to the US market, helping them solve complex global logistics challenges and expand with confidence. This role offers exposure to mid-market and high-growth accounts, with opportunities to build deep commercial and product expertise in global logistics technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you additionally need to know:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;This is a full-time, onsite role based in our Bengaluru (MG Road) office. The role follows US collaboration hours (7:30PM–4:30AM IST) to support seamless cross-regional execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What would be you be responsible for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Owning the end-to-end sales cycle for outbound opportunities across e-commerce, marketplaces, and high-volume online sellers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting outbound prospecting via calls, email, LinkedIn, and CRM workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Running discovery calls to understand customer shipping, fulfilment, and logistics requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Presenting and positioning Easyship’s shipping software, warehousing, and fulfilment solutions, with a strong focus on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;US market&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing pipeline progression, forecasting, and deal execution through to close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating closely with Product, Tech, Operations, and Customer Success teams to ensure smooth handover and onboarding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining accurate and up-to-date records in HubSpot CRM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with marketing and partnerships to support campaigns and outbound motions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staying informed on trends in global logistics, e-commerce fulfilment, and shipping technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Might Be a Good Fit If…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 2+ years’ experience in a closing sales role, ideally in&amp;nbsp;SaaS, logistics, shipping, or e-commerce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience owning deals end-to-end, including pipeline generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have exposure to&amp;nbsp;shipping software, fulfilment, or global logistics&amp;nbsp;is strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have understanding of or experience selling into the&amp;nbsp;US market&amp;nbsp;is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have strong discovery, presentation, and negotiation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable using HubSpot, LinkedIn, and sales enablement tools (e.g. Gong, Outreach)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are highly organised, self-motivated, and comfortable working across global time zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

