&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Easyship:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Easyship is one of the world&#39;s leading multi-carrier shipping software, built to make global eCommerce borderless. Since 2014, we&#39;ve been on a mission to democratize logistics by removing the &quot;black box&quot; of international shipping costs and complexities. Trusted by over 100,000 brands, our platform provides a single &quot;mission control&quot; for global trade, offering access to 550+ courier services across 200+ destinations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;We are an award-winning, global team (Forbes 30 Under 30, TechInAsia&#39;s Best Startup) with offices in London, New York, Hong Kong, and beyond. We&#39;re growing fast, we value transparency, and we genuinely enjoy building the infrastructure that powers modern commerce. If you&#39;re ready to solve complex problems at scale, we&#39;d love to have you join us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sales Manager (Player/Coach)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;: London&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting to:&lt;/strong&gt; Director, Commercial &amp;amp; Marketing. &lt;br&gt;Key&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Relationships:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sales Team, Customers, Marketing, Customer Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Easyship is a shipping technology platform that connects sellers and marketplaces to couriers, and we build customized end-to-end logistics solutions for the world&#39;s fastest-growing brands. As we move upmarket, our enterprise sales team is closing larger, more complex deals, and we need a leader to drive it. We&#39;re looking for a Sales Manager to lead a team of enterprise Account Executives, owning their performance, coaching, and execution against high-value, multi-stakeholder deals. We&#39;re after a player-coach who knows eCommerce and shipping, has carried and led enterprise quota, and gets energy from developing reps and sharpening the GTM motion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What would you be responsible for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
