&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you additionally need to know:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;This is a full-time, onsite role based in our Bengaluru (MG Road) office. The role follows US collaboration hours (10:00 PM–7:00 AM IST) to support seamless cross-regional execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What would be you be responsible for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1. Incident Management &amp;amp; Client Advocacy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
